<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Bienvenue sur Swingcars!</title>
	<link rel="icon" href="../assets/img/icons/superklok.ico">
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bangers&family=Caveat+Brush&family=Lacquer&family=Lobster&family=Lobster+Two:ital@1&family=Metal+Mania&family=Righteous&family=Sedgwick+Ave+Display&family=UnifrakturMaguntia&family=VT323&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/nav.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/btn.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/app.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/home.css">
</head>
<body class="d-flex text-center vh-100 text-white">
	<div class="cover-container d-flex w-100 h-100 py-3 px-0 px-md-3 mx-auto flex-column">
		<header class="mb-auto navText">
			<div class="d-none d-md-block">
				<h3 class="navbar-brand float-start mb-0 neonBtn">Swingcars.ca</h3>
				<nav class="nav nav-masthead justify-content-center float-end">
					<% if(!currentUser) { %>
					<a class="neonBtn me-4 mt-1" href="/login">Connexion</a>
					<a class="neonBtn me-4 mt-1" href="/register">Inscription</a>
					<% } else { %>
					<a class="neonBtn me-4 mt-1" href="/logout">D&eacute;connexion</a>
					<% } %>
				</nav>
			</div>
		</header>
		<main class="pb-5">
			<h1 class="lgText neonBtn mb-3">Swingcars</h1>
			<p class="lead smText contentFont">Bienvenue sur Swingcars!<br>D&eacute;couvrez la vie &agrave; travers la voiture de quelqu'un d'autre.<br>* Les membres doivent poss&eacute;der un permis de conduire en cours de validit&eacute;.*</p>
			<a href="/voitures" class="neonBtn enterBtn">Entrez &agrave; l'int&eacute;rieur</a>
		</main>
		<footer class="footer mt-auto">
			<div class="container d-none d-lg-block">
				<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/copyright') %>
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/trevmorin') %>
					<div class="ms-auto">
						<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/social4') %>
						<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/social3') %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="container d-none d-sm-block d-lg-none">
				<div class="d-flex align-items-center pb-1">
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/trevmorin') %>
					<div class="ms-auto">
						<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/social4') %>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex align-items-center">
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/copyright') %>
					<div class="ms-auto pb-1">
						<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/social3') %>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="d-block d-sm-none">
				<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pb-2">
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/trevmorin') %>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pb-2">
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/copyright') %>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pt-2">
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/social4') %>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center pt-1">
					<%- partial('partials/hpbuttons/social3') %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</div>
	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>